OL,7,FA man who chanted about Hillsborough
OL,8,Fon the eve of the disaster has been
OL,9,Fbanned from all football games for
OL,10,Fthree years.
OL,12,FStuart Rutter, 41, was found guilty
OL,13,Fafter trial after he began the tragedy
OL,14,Fchanting outside the main stand of
OL,15,FAnfield Stadium where he was attending
OL,16,Fthe Liverpool v Crystal Palace game.
