OL,7,FSouth Sefton Magistrates Court heard
OL,8,Fthat on 14 April, the eve of the 35th
OL,9,Fanniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,10,FDisaster, Rutter began chanting which
OL,11,Fcaused alarm and distress to people
OL,12,Fattending the game.
OL,14,FOfficers arrested and charged Rutter,
OL,15,Fwho is a Crystal Palace fan, with
OL,16,FSection 5 Public Order offence.
OL,18,FRutter, of Sutton Coldfield in the
OL,19,FWest Midlands, was issued with the
OL,20,Fthree-year order, #500 compensation
OL,21,Fpenalty and other fines.
