OL,7,FChief Inspector Iain Wyke said: "This
OL,8,Ftype of behaviour has no place in
OL,9,Ffootball. We will take action and
OL,10,Fidentify those who commit hate crime
OL,11,Fin any form, and this includes
OL,12,Funacceptable chanting which causes
OL,13,Fdistress to others.
OL,15,F"Merseyside Police will work to
OL,16,Fidentify and bring to justice anyone
OL,17,Ffound responsible for committing a
OL,18,Fhate crime.
